item.description:
Volunteer Appreciation Day, October 13th (9:30 - 2:30)- Chairman needed

Coordinated by the Chamber of Commerce we are invited to have a booth to promote the Jaycees to the community.  Event runs from 10-2  p.m.  

"Come by and bring the kids for a thank you from South Windsor to all Volunteers.  There will be Hamburgers, hot dogs, bounce house, cotton candy, and popcorn.  There will also be a large side walk sale at Geisslers generating some foot traffic from the public, so we will have a Jaycess table as well handing out information for potential new members and explaining all that we do for the community."
item.name: Volunteer Appreciation Day
